name: Jedi Guardian
Lore: 'A Jedi may choose to intervene in the natural course of events, but must accept responsibility for the consequences.',
Text: 'Never deploys if Inner Strength on table.  Deploys +3 unless We''ll Handle This (or Duel Of The Fates) on table.  Whenever this Jedi uses a lightsaber to hit a character, opponent loses 1 Force.  Immune to attrition < 4.',
